  "title": "ISic002123. Funerary inscription",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/93BBRA2N\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/93BBRA2N</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>🞣 κοιμήσις <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κηπιον\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κηπιον\">Κηπιον</span></span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυρια\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυρια\">Κυρια</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυριλλα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυριλλα\">Κυριλλα̣</span></span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/93BBRA2N\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/93BBRA2N</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>🞣ΚΟΙΜΗΣΙΣ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κηπιον\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κηπιον\">ΚΗΠΙΟΝ</span></span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυρια\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυρια\">ΚΥΡΙΑ</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κυριλλα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Κυριλλα\">ΚΥΡΙΛΛ.</span></span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic002123_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-28\" src=\"ISic002123_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic002123.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo J. Prag 2023-07-28\" src=\"ISic002123-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text after Meligunis Lipara VII</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The inscription is reported in ML VII and earlier publications by Bernabò Brea, but does not seem to have been registered in SEG and is not included in ML XII</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Bernabò Brea 1988 96-97, figs. 54-55 (ph) </li><li> Bernabò Brea and Cavalier 1994 26-27 fig.6 (dr) <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002156\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002156</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>lunate letters with tendency to cursive</p> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
